statements: SELECT * FROM warehouse_performance_metrics;
SELECT order_date, fulfillment_time_mins FROM warehouse_performance_metrics;
SELECT * FROM warehouse_performance_metrics WHERE order_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT order_id, fulfillment_time_mins FROM warehouse_performance_metrics ORDER BY fulfillment_time_mins DESC;
SELECT COUNT(order_id) AS total_orders FROM warehouse_performance_metrics;
SELECT * FROM warehouse_performance_metrics WHERE fulfillment_time_mins > 60 ORDER BY order_date DESC;
SELECT order_id, order_date FROM warehouse_performance_metrics WHERE order_id BETWEEN 100 AND 200 ORDER BY fulfillment_time_mins ASC;
SELECT * FROM warehouse_performance_metrics WHERE fulfillment_time_mins < 30 AND order_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY fulfillment_time_mins DESC, order_date ASC;
SELECT AVG(fulfillment_time_mins) AS avg_fulfillment_time FROM warehouse_performance_metrics;
SELECT MAX(fulfillment_time_mins) AS max_fulfillment_time, MIN(fulfillment_time_mins) AS min_fulfillment_time FROM warehouse_performance_metrics;
